reviews.text:
Food was nothing special, service was nowhere professional.
Still find it hard to believe the chefs can swear on most if not every sentence they chat and play on their phones(which they swiftly put them on dishes they used to serve my grilled chicken with) right at their public cooking counter throughout my 40mins there. Not all of us, or any of us, will be interested in how many underwear you bring for your two weeks trip to Japan to learn how to make Okonomiyaki.

Definitely not going there again. Ever.
A little bit expensive with OK food.  Quite authentic Osaka taste but food portion is quite small given that it is quite pricey

Not terrible. Nothing to be excited about either.

Newly open today, tasty food, good service ,
Cosy environmet .
Worth to try and would come again

Many restaurants in food court with different cuisine 
At affordable prices

Fun unique mall. Lots of cute themed characters around and the environment is very different from that of a typical mall. The stores here are more items based than clothing and are unique. Everything in here is more cartoon based.
Interesting mall tailored for young people.
This mall of many small shops mostly sells trivial souvenirs of nothing. This is not the place to go for anything practical. Useless distractions are not for those of a more puritanical disposition.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角彌敦道700號
result.name: T.O.P This is Our Place

reviews.text:
鋪頭都幾多 同埋好多都係唔同種類
但好似唔多岩男仔
上次同男朋友行個陣
佢都話無咩岩佢
這個都算是新開的商場，在假日的時間，人流暢旺，特別是很多家傭流連的關係，女洗手間多人使用不在話下，連wi-fi 都無辦法連上，那麼~管理層便要想法子提升網絡容量！
彌敦道700號位於香港九龍旺角彌敦道700號，樓高23層，1984年至2015年由香港政府持有，2016年起由領展房地產投資信託基金持有。 項目於2018年6月開業，商場定名為T.O.P This is Our Place。商場位處旺角核心範圍，將以年輕、活力、動感及帶領潮流打造旺角地標。
應有盡有，接連旺角中心，方便購物。 值得一提係T.O.P有個放空空間， 唔落雨可以去坐吓，感覺舒服。
